<p>

Viewing this site with Netscape? If so, then try the Fun Facts puzzle...hidden
throughout the LNC site are eight puzzle pieces. Each time you find one, click
on it to receive a fun fact and add the piece to the puzzle. If you collect all
of the pieces, you will be entered into our monthly drawing to win a sweatshirt
from <a href="http://www.TheLincolnMuseum.org/">The Lincoln Museum</a>.

<blockquote>
Note: Sorry, but our fun facts puzzle is only available to Netscape browsers.
If you would like to enter the contest and don't have a copy of Netscape please
send mail to:
<p>
